---
title: Chinese Sweet Chilli Tofu Tacos with Crunchy Slaw
description: Turn a Chinese-inspired meal of glazed tofu cubes, crisp slaw and fresh cucumber into delicious tacos brimming with flavour and colour! It's a multicultural feast that you'll crave - and it's on the table in a flash!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c108a68e3f33959d75c6813-b593e830.jpg
